I hope you at least enjoyed speedrunning a bit,here are few tips from a fellow who speedran MC few,,,(dot dot dot) times so you will be less furious, i hope it helps:
1,There are tutorials on youtube for the lava + water bucket lava placement(i used those to learn) for a nether portal
2,Always be en-guarde(ready to do quick action) in nether,like MLG boat/MLG haybale/shield block from projectiles or block of lava that can surprise you,lack of doing that killed COUNTLESS MC speedrunners MANY times

3,Ender dragon is like a bull and you need to do MLG water buckets alot as a result + destroy tops of the pillars,if you dont finish him with beds strategy
4,You dont need emeralds unless you trade with villagers early on and you need alot of gold to get that meme"Dreamluck" by piglin trade for enderpearls
5,End portal is always around few hundred blocks away from spawn,you can get there with ender eyes(ender pearls and blaze powder mixup),always get more ender eyes than needed cause some may break midway

Bonus that is worth research:
In vanilla single player 1,16's you can duplicate items using a save and quit glitch,but i dunno if they still allow use of glitches on the leaderboard so take it with a grain of salt

Good luck,best shark girl
